---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | BharatAo" description="How BharatAo handles your data.">
  <div class="wrap section" style="max-width:760px;">
    <h1 class="article-title" style="font-family:var(--font-display);color:var(--ba-heading);">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>BharatAo does not currently collect any personal data beyond an
       optional email address if you sign up to be notified at launch. That
       email is used only to send you a launch notification and is never
       sold or shared with third parties.</p>
    <p>Once the site is live with advertising and analytics, this page will
       be updated to describe exactly what's collected (e.g. anonymized
       analytics, ad-related cookies) before those features go live.</p>
    <p>Questions: <a href="mailto:support@facenova.uk">support@facenova.uk</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
